  --porcelain:#FCFCFB; --ink:#1C1B1A; --ink-muted:#6E6A66;
  --plum:#7A5C6E; --plum-deep:#4A3340; --plum-tint:#F0E9ED;
  --stone:#E4DDD6; --surface:#FFFFFF;
  --sage:#5E7A6B; --clay:#B5894E; --rosewood:#9B5C5C;
  --radius:12px; --radius-lg:16px;
}
```
Fonts: Cormorant Garamond (500,600) + Hanken Grotesk (400,500) via next/font/google,
